者同意討論自殺的人並不會真的自殺。調查又發現，男性、年長及教育程度較低者對自殺存在較多迷思。「2019香港精神月」籌委會指上述迷思不盡正確，當局應作針對性宣傳。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191010/s00001/1570645544467/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191010%2Fs00001%2F1570645544467%2F&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ca892b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191010%2Fs00001%2F1570645544467%2F&h=83300990\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191010/s00001/1570645544467/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"依啲老母唔要都罷"}]}